      "settings": {
        "width": "full-width",
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h2>FAQs about Police Lights</h2><h3>Q1: Are your police lights street-legal for civilian vehicles?</h3><p>Some lights may be used for off-road or show purposes, but use on public roads is regulated. Always check your local laws.</p><h3>Q2: Do the lights come with flash pattern options?</h3><p>Yes. Most of our LED police lights include multiple built-in flash patterns that can be easily programmed.</p><h3>Q3: Are your police lights waterproof?</h3><p>Absolutely. Our lights are built with weather-resistant or waterproof housings designed to perform in rain, snow, and extreme temperatures.</p><h3>Q4: Can I sync multiple lights together?</h3><p>Yes. Many of our police lights include sync functionality so multiple units can flash in coordinated patterns.</p><h3>Q5: Do you offer installation support?</h3><p>Yes. We offer wiring guides and technical support to help ensure your installation is smooth and secure.</p>",
        "heading_size": "medium",
        "text_alignment": "left"
      }
